fulltitle: Church Committee: FBI "Black Bag" Break Ins (B3.S6)
title: Church Committee: FBI "Black Bag" Break Ins (B3.S6)
description:
'Our Hidden History' Audiobooks: https://sellfy.com/OurHiddenHistory More Church Committee Reports: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBINnEpNu5u5DDKZr3zRDb9v_Q2pV55dA ---- This is an audio recording of a section of the Final Report of the United States' Senate Church Committee, officially known as the United States Senate Select Committee to Study Governmental Operations with Respect to Intelligence Activities) on Intelligence Activities and the Rights of Americans (Book 3 of the Church Committee Report). This is a recording of Section 6 of Book 3, WARRANTLESS SURREPTITIOUS ENTRIES: FBI "BLACK BAG" BREAK-INS AND MICROPHONE INSTALLATIONS.

For the full book, visit the Mary Ferrell Foundation: https://www.maryferrell.org/showDoc.html?docId=1159&relPageId=740&search=church_committee%20book%203

Produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History' and Narrated by Chris Abernathy (https://www.fiverr.com/provoman).

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
